{"timestamp": "2026-06-27T16:14:49.539611+00:00", "role": "tutor", "raw_response": {"id": "-PY_arzQAcHsjrEP543qwAE", "created": 1782576887, "model": "gemini-2.5-pro", "object": "chat.completion", "system_fingerprint": null, "choices": [{"finish_reason": "stop", "index": 0, "message": {"content": "嗯，听起来很合理。如果树长大的物质都来自土壤，那土壤肯定会变少。\n\n很久以前，有一位科学家也这么想。他做了一个实验，把一棵小树种在盆里，五年后，树长大了非常多，但他发现土的重量几乎没变。\n\n你觉得这个实验说明了什么？", "role": "assistant", "tool_calls": null, "function_call": null, "images": [], "thinking_blocks": []}}], "usage": {"completion_tokens": 76, "prompt_tokens": 533, "total_tokens": 609, "completion_tokens_details": {"text_tokens": 76}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": null, "text_tokens": 533, "image_tokens": null, "video_tokens": null}, "cache_read_input_tokens": null}, "vertex_ai_grounding_metadata": [], "vertex_ai_url_context_metadata": [], "vertex_ai_safety_results": [], "vertex_ai_citation_metadata": [], "service_tier": "default"}}
