{"timestamp": "2026-06-27T16:15:03.117837+00:00", "role": "tutor", "raw_response": {"id": "Afc_aoDJLP_1jrEP_r-gyAE", "created": 1782576897, "model": "gemini-2.5-pro", "object": "chat.completion", "system_fingerprint": null, "choices": [{"finish_reason": "stop", "index": 0, "message": {"content": "好问题！既然实验说明主要不是来自土壤，那我们就得想想别的可能性。\n\n植物生长，除了需要土壤里的养分，还需要什么别的东西呢？", "role": "assistant", "tool_calls": null, "function_call": null, "images": [], "thinking_blocks": []}}], "usage": {"completion_tokens": 557, "prompt_tokens": 626, "total_tokens": 1183, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 522, "text_tokens": 35}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": null, "text_tokens": 626, "image_tokens": null, "video_tokens": null}, "cache_read_input_tokens": null}, "vertex_ai_grounding_metadata": [], "vertex_ai_url_context_metadata": [], "vertex_ai_safety_results": [], "vertex_ai_citation_metadata": [], "service_tier": "default"}}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-27T16:15:11.675250+00:00", "role": "student", "raw_response": {"id": "B_c_ao38D5G9jrEP08_PkAI", "created": 1782576903, "model": "gemini-2.5-pro", "object": "chat.completion", "system_fingerprint": null, "choices": [{"finish_reason": "stop", "index": 0, "message": {"content": "我还是不明白，难道是水吗？", "role": "assistant", "tool_calls": null, "function_call": null, "images": [], "thinking_blocks": []}}], "usage": {"completion_tokens": 948, "prompt_tokens": 405, "total_tokens": 1353, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 938, "text_tokens": 10}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": null, "text_tokens": 405, "image_tokens": null, "video_tokens": null}, "cache_read_input_tokens": null}, "vertex_ai_grounding_metadata": [], "vertex_ai_url_context_metadata": [], "vertex_ai_safety_results": [], "vertex_ai_citation_metadata": [], "service_tier": "default"}}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-27T16:15:24.578468+00:00", "role": "tutor", "raw_response": {"id": "D_c_asevNNSTjrEP9Zi42QE", "created": 1782576911, "model": "gemini-2.5-pro", "object": "chat.completion", "system_fingerprint": null, "choices": [{"finish_reason": "stop", "index": 0, "message": {"content": "你说到了一个非常重要的东西！植物的生长确实离不开水。\n\n不过，构成树干和树叶的那些固体物质，主要是一种叫做纤维素的东西，它的成分和水很不一样。\n\n所以，水是必须的，但它不是最主要的‘建筑材料’。植物还需要从别的地方获取原料。想一想，除了土壤和水，植物还暴露在什么环境中？", "role": "assistant", "tool_calls": null, "function_call": null, "images": [], "thinking_blocks": []}}], "usage": {"completion_tokens": 1508, "prompt_tokens": 673, "total_tokens": 2181, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 1423, "text_tokens": 85}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": null, "text_tokens": 673, "image_tokens": null, "video_tokens": null}, "cache_read_input_tokens": null}, "vertex_ai_grounding_metadata": [], "vertex_ai_url_context_metadata": [], "vertex_ai_safety_results": [], "vertex_ai_citation_metadata": [], "service_tier": "default"}}
